                    <list>
                      <item xml:id="e1"><desc><locus target="#ir #iv" facs="001 002">Fols. ir, iv</locus>Blank</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="e2"><desc><locus target="#15v #16r" facs="017">Fols. 15v, 16r</locus>Spaces for the names of the patriarchs left blank</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a1"><desc><locus target="#18v" facs="020">Fol. 18v</locus>Mentions <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8388SalamaI">Salāmā III</persName></desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a2"><desc><locus target="#20r" facs="021">Fol. 20r</locus>Mentions Wäldä ʾƎsraʿel (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ እስራኤል፡</foreign>)</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a3"><desc><locus target="#22r" facs="023">Fol. 22r</locus>Mentions Wäldä Maryam (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign>) and Wäldä ʾƎsraʿel (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ እስራኤል፡</foreign>)</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a4"><desc><locus target="#31v" facs="033">Fol. 31v</locus>Mentions Wäldä ʾÄbsabyos (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ አብሳብዮስ፡</foreign>) and Wäldä Maryam (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign>)</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a5"><desc><locus target="#31v #32r" facs="033">Fols. 31v, 32r</locus>Mentions  <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3258CyrilIV">Cyril IV</persName> and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8388SalamaI">Salāmā III</persName></desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="e3"><desc><locus target="#33v" facs="035">Fol. 33v</locus>Space for the name of the king is left blank</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a6"><desc><locus target="#38r" facs="039">Fol. 38r</locus>A prayer for Gäbrä Hana (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ገብረ፡ ሃና፡</foreign>), ʾÄskalä Gäbrǝʾel (<foreign xml:lang="gez">አስካለ፡ ገብርኤል፡</foreign>), Wäldä ʾÄbsabyos, and Wäldä ʾƎsraʿel.</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a7"><desc><locus target="#43r" facs="044">Fol. 43r</locus>Mentions Wäldä ʾƎsraʿel and ʾÄskalä Gäbrǝʾel.</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a8"><desc><locus target="#43v #45r" facs="045 046">Fols. 43v, 45r</locus>Mentions Wäldä ʾÄbsabyos and his beloved Wäldä ʾƎsraʿel and his brother ʾÄskalä Gäbrǝʾel</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a9"><desc type="ScribalSignature"><locus target="#45r" facs="046">Fol. 45r</locus>Mentions the scribe Wäldä Maryam (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign>)</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a10"><desc><locus target="#49r" facs="050">Fol. 49r</locus>Contains a list of names of people who prayed the prayer.</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="e4"><desc><locus target="#38 #42" facs="039 043">Fols. 38, 42</locus>Navigation system: white string sewn into fore edge</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="e5"><desc>Numbered quire 2–5.</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="e6"><desc>
                        Scribal intervention:
                        words of text are written interlinearly, <locus target="#1v #4r #5r #9v #21v" facs="003 005 006 011 023">folss. 1v, 4r, 5r, 9v, 21v, </locus>, etc.;
                        text has been removed, <locus target="#20v #35v #36r" facs="022 037">20v, 35v, 36r</locus></desc></item>
